{"word":"H4799 - מָרַח - mârach - maw-rakh' - Lay for a plaister","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מָרַח</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>mârach"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>maw-rakh'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Lay for a plaister"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பற்றுப்போடுதல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"(Qal) to rub"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>soften</i> by rubbing or pressure; hence (medicinally) to <i>apply</i> as an emollient: - lay for a plaister."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}